article.headline: Hamilton scores 34, High Point downs Radford 99-74

images.name: Radford Highlanders vs. High Point Panthers: Game Highlights
images.caption: Radford Highlanders vs. High Point Panthers: Game Highlights

article.linkText: Hamilton scores 34, High Point downs Radford 99-74
article.story: HIGH POINT, N.C. -- — Kimani Hamilton's 34 points led High Point past Radford 99-74 on Saturday night. Hamilton was 13 of 16 shooting, including 6 for 8 from 3-point range, and went 2 for 4 from the line for the Panthers (22-6, 11-2 Big South Conference). Abdoulaye Thiam scored 21 points and Titas Sargiunas had 12 points. Kenyon Giles finished with 24 points and four assists for the Highlanders (13-14, 3-9). Radford also got 11 points and six rebounds from Josiah Harris. DaQuan Smith recorded 11 points and five assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
